[[Image:野見宿禰.jpg|thumb|200px|Nomi no Sukune]]
{{nihongo|'''Nomi no Sukune'''|野見 宿禰}} was a Japanese legendary sumo wrestler during [[Emperor Suinin]] era. He kicked and killed his opponent. It wasn't modern sumo, but he is regarded as the organiser of sumo in human. He was an ancestor of [[Sugawara no Michizane]].

